  <p>NOTICE:</p>

  <p>The â€˜pygmentsâ€™ highlighter is currently unsupported on GitHub Pages. I use â€˜rougeâ€™ for highlighting instead. 
If some of you receive the email of â€˜Page build warningâ€™ from GitHub, to suppress this warning, change the â€˜highlighterâ€™ value to â€˜rougeâ€™ in your â€˜_config.ymlâ€™.</p>
